data.title: Arnold Schwarzenegger's Pets
data.meta_description: Gustav Date of birth: Adopted in 2000 Breed: Chocolate Labrador Whiskey Date of birth: Adopted 2019 Breed: Miniature Horse Lulu Date of birth: Birthday April 28 - Adopted 2019 Breed: Miniature Donkey Schnitzel Date of birth: Adopted Dec 2021 Breed: Leonberger Dutch Date of birth: Adopted Jul 2020 Breed: Alaskan malamut
data.text:
GUSTAV: Arnold Schwarzenegger, the renowned actor and former bodybuilder, had a beloved Chocolate Labrador named Gustav, which he named after his father. While Gustav was part of Schwarzenegger's life in the late 2000s, there has been no recent mention of him, leading us to assume that Gustav has since passed away.

Lulu: On Lulu's special day, Arnold Schwarzenegger showcased his love by singing the birthday song in his iconic Terminator voice. Lulu and Whiskey, another dog in his household, enjoy the freedom to roam around Schwarzenegger's home. They have even joined him during workout sessions, embracing an active lifestyle reminiscent of Schwarzenegger's days as Mr. Universe.

Whiskey: Originally owned by his daughter Katherine, Whiskey the pony somehow found her way into Arnold Schwarzenegger's house. Schwarzenegger revealed that Whiskey made herself comfortable around the house, but disliked being left alone in the stable for sleep.

SCHNITZEL: In December 2021, Arnold Schwarzenegger welcomed a new furry companion named Schnitzel into his life. The dog, a Leonberger breed, shares a name with Schwarzenegger's favorite Austrian dish, showcasing his appreciation for both his culture and his four-legged friend.

DUTCH: In July 2020, Arnold Schwarzenegger adopted Dutch, a dog named after his iconic character in the film "Predator." Dutch's appearance resembles that of an Alaskan malamute or a malamute mix.

CHERRY: Arnold Schwarzenegger also has a lovable Yorkshire Terrier named Cherry, who was rescued and became a cherished part of his family.

SCHNELLY: The most recent addition to Arnold Schwarzenegger's furry family is Schnelly, a tiny pig. Schwarzenegger adopted Schnelly in April 2023, and the adorable pig is often seen alongside his dog, Cherry.
